# Framework philosophy wrapper

Always read and follow **[PHILOSOPHY.md](../../PHILOSOPHY.md)** first.

- Do not introduce custom macro event loops.
- Keep physics logic in compiled `StMaker` classes.
- Keep analysis behavior YAML-driven (`mainconf` + referenced configs).
- Avoid hardcoded cut or threshold values.

Project operational rules are maintained in:

- [docs/ai/AGENT_RULES.md](../../docs/ai/AGENT_RULES.md)

In case of conflict, `PHILOSOPHY.md` is the source of truth.
